mods.abstract: Mr. William Charles Macready (1793-1873) in the role of Cardinal Wolsey quotes "What's this___To the Pope? The letter, as I live, with all the business I writ to his Holiness, Nay then, farewell! I have touch'd the highest point of all my greatness," in Henry VIII Act 3 Scene 2. Engraved from the Original by C.H. Jeens. The London Printing and Publishing Company.
